{"tid":2178594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"晚市堂食放寬至晚上 9時 有市民稱期待外出晚膳","createTime":"2020-08-28T13:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T13:23:26.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d45ec054e8bb5ee7b8a781469db5748ff85d5579","tid":2178594,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"晚市堂食放寬至晚上 9時 有市民稱期待外出晚膳<br />\n2020-08-28 HKT 18:51<br />\n<br />\n&quot;政府放寬部分社交距離措施，暫停一個半月的晚市堂食恢復至晚上 9時。有市民表示，期待外出晚膳，亦有市民表示因為疫情，未必會去外出......主要做堂食生意的西餐廳負責人張小姐說，禁晚市堂食以來，生意下跌九成，形容只靠一成生意和積蓄維持餐廳運作......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546537-20200828.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546537-20200828.htm&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=2ee5b987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546537-20200828.htm&h=904d608b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546537-20200828.htm</a>"},{"pid":"19e3047a0ca4b436fd1baf9ccb904b9df8944050","tid":2178594,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"經過見到間間都要等位"}]}